34:44.460 --> 34:45.773
I don't know that
I've ever had it.

34:45.806 --> 34:47.670
It's like, I used to
really like kale,

34:47.706 --> 34:49.183
I used to love kale, but now I
don't want to eat it because...

34:49.190 --> 34:50.777
