34:50.812 --> 34:53.263
They're making, like,
smoothies out of the shit.

34:53.297 --> 34:54.989
Are we doing steak?

34:55.023 --> 34:56.956
If we can do steak,
that's what you eat...

34:56.991 --> 34:59.821
That's... that's what we have.

34:59.856 --> 35:01.029
Yeah.

35:01.064 --> 35:03.135
Yeah, I was thinking
just off the top of my head.

35:03.170 --> 35:05.344
"What do I want tonight?
Uh...

35:05.379 --> 35:07.415
How about meat?
