I know where to go.
I've actually never been.

35:14.560 --> 35:16.493
This friend told me about it.

35:16.528 --> 35:19.945
But the funny thing,
it's a drive-thru.

35:19.979 --> 35:21.153
Drive-thru steak?

35:25.330 --> 35:27.642
I know.
Like, I'm... surprised as you are.

35:27.677 --> 35:29.782
Cocktails? Do we get
cocktails in the drive-thru?

35:29.817 --> 35:32.820
I doubt it, but I'm sure
we can get some beer.

35:32.854 --> 35:35.063
- All right, steak it is.
- Let's do it.

