36:10.754 --> 36:13.343
I think they use this
in the desert.

36:13.378 --> 36:17.175
Yeah, they're pretty common
here, right, like, on the beach?

36:17.209 --> 36:18.693
Not good for winter.

36:18.728 --> 36:21.248
No.

36:21.282 --> 36:21.782
♪

